      "writtenOn": "2020-03-18T13:58:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We have:\n - glog\n - cloud logging (which currently always falls back to glog)\n - cloud logging v2, which IIUC is completely independent and only used in TD\n - slog, which has a single implementation that can either not log or log to stderr\n - new in a followup CL: JSON adapter logger",
      "parentUuid": "0e1e8f03_8fe6a37b",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 97,
