      "message": "\"raw logs\" \u003d\u003d slog (unless I\u0027m misunderstanding, which is very possible)\n\n\u003e The plan is to use the JSON adapter and just dump JSON to stdout for this use case?\n\nYes, JSON adapter to slog.\n\nAll the above sounds correct, with the caveat that I find it very scary to change logging implementations, so at least for all of these CLs, I tried to make them no-ops.",
      "parentUuid": "58bea633_559fb498",
